des: Venice Vibes is Venice Magazine's virtual, voice-guided experience, featuring photos, stories, and information on events that are happening in Fort Lauderdale. If you're on a video device, you can view incredible photos and fashion stories and immerse yourself in a voice-guided, luxury experience.
